<item>
            <title>[HADOOP-10401] ShellBasedUnixGroupsMapping#getGroups does not always return primary group first</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HADOOP-10401</link>
                <project id="12310240" key="HADOOP">Hadoop Common</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;tt&gt;ShellBasedUnixGroupsMapping#getGroups&lt;/tt&gt; does not always return the primary group first.  It should do this so that clients who expect it don&apos;t get the wrong result.  We should also document that the primary group is returned first in the API.  Note that &lt;tt&gt;JniBasedUnixGroupsMapping&lt;/tt&gt; does return the primary group first.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12700629">HADOOP-10401</key>
